@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wciled(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(0.76)
    tmp = (wp.sin(v2) * (wp.exp(v0 + 0.16) + (tmp + 0.79 - tmp + 0.97)))
    v0 = v2
    tmp = wp.exp(0.18)
    v1 = ((0.19 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.54)) / wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.51)))
    v2 = (0.43 - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.63) + (v1 + 0.50 * v2 + 0.53)))
    data[tid] = v0
